The paper deals with secure and efficient querying of encrypted databases, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of cryptography (cs.CR), databases (cs.DB), and security and privacy (cs.CY, cs.DS, cs.SE). The paper proposes novel secure comparison and range query protocols, which are fundamental building blocks in secure database querying. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CR, followed by cs.DB, cs.CY, cs.DS, and cs.SE.
